\"inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center gap-2 border font-medium whitespace-nowrap transition-all duration-200 outline-none select-none focus-visible:border-ring focus-visible:ring-3 focus-visible:ring-ring/40 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg]:size-4 border-border/80 bg-secondary/70 text-foreground shadow-[inset_0_1px_0_rgba(255,255,255,0.24)] backdrop-blur-sm backdrop-saturate-[1.3] hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-primary/20 hover:bg-secondary text-sm size-10 rounded-full p-0\" aria-label=\"Open menu\" type=\"button\" aria-haspopup=\"dialog\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"radix-_R_99lb_\" data-state=\"closed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu size-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 5h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 12h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 19h16\"></path></svg></button></div></div></div></header><main id=\"content\" class=\"flex-1\"><section class=\"relative overflow-hidden pt-32 pb-[4.5rem] sm:pt-36 sm:pb-[5.5rem] lg:pt-40 lg:pb-24\"><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute top-[-10%] left-[18%] h-64 w-64 rounded-full bg-[var(--hero-orbit)] blur-3xl md:h-80 md:w-80\"></div><div class=\"absolute top-[6%] right-[12%] h-56 w-56 rounded-full bg-[var(--hero-spotlight)] blur-3xl md:h-72 md:w-72\"></div><div class=\"absolute inset-x-[18%] top-[-14%] h-72 rounded-full bg-white/28 blur-3xl dark:bg-white/6\"></div></div><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"pointer-events-none h-full w-full fill-current stroke-current hero-grid-mask absolute inset-0 text-foreground/10\"><defs><pattern id=\"_R_hav5ulb_\" width=\"44\" height=\"44\" patternUnits=\"userSpaceOnUse\" x=\"-1\" y=\"-1\"><path d=\"M.5 44V.5H44\" fill=\"none\" stroke-dasharray=\"0\"></path></pattern></defs><rect width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" fill=\"url(#_R_hav5ulb_)\"></rect><svg x=\"-1\" y=\"-1\" class=\"overflow-visible\"></svg></svg><div class=\"absolute inset-x-0 bottom-0 h-28 bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent to-background\"></div><div class=\"mx-auto w-full max-w-7xl px-5 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative\"><div class=\"max-w-5xl\"><div class=\"space-y-6\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full border px-3 py-1 text-[0.72rem] font-medium tracking-[0.13em] uppercase transition-colors border-primary/40 bg-primary text-white backdrop-blur-sm backdrop-saturate-[1.4]\">Projects</div><div class=\"space-y-4 sm:space-y-5\"><h1 class=\"hero-title max-w-5xl\">Capability, shown through the systems we build.</h1><p class=\"copy-lg max-w-3xl\">Products, platforms, internal systems, and open-source infrastructure with visible design judgment.</p></div><div class=\"grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-2 sm:max-w-3xl\"><div class=\"rounded-[1.3rem] border border-border/60 bg-background/38 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-foreground/66\">Operational platforms</div><div class=\"rounded-[1.3rem] border border-border/60 bg-background/38 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-foreground/66\">Developer-facing products</div><div class=\"rounded-[1.3rem] border border-border/60 bg-background/38 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-foreground/66\">Open-source ecosystems</div></div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row sm:flex-wrap\"><a class=\"inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-full border font-medium whitespace-nowrap transition-all duration-200 outline-none select-none focus-visible:border-ring focus-visible:ring-3 focus-visible:ring-ring/40 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg]:size-4 border-transparent bg-[linear-gradient(135deg,#4d35ef_0%,#432dd7_100%)] text-white shadow-[0_14px_40px_rgba(67,45,215,0.28)] hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-[0_20px_54px_rgba(67,45,215,0.36)] h-12 px-6 text-[0.95rem]\" href=\"/contact\">Talk through your system</a></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"section-space\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-full max-w-7xl px-5 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 space-y-10\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"max-w-3xl space-y-5\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full border px-3 py-1 text-[0.72rem] font-medium tracking-[0.13em] uppercase transition-colors border-border/70 bg-background/52 text-foreground/62 backdrop-blur-sm backdrop-saturate-[1.3]\">Selected archetypes</div><div class=\"space-y-4\"><h2 class=\"section-title\">Real categories of work, not fictional case studies.</h2><p class=\"section-copy\">Archetypes that show the kind of system thinking Sonicverse brings to a project.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"rounded-[1.9rem] border border-border/70 bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,var(--surface-1),var(--surface-2))] shadow-[var(--shadow-soft)] backdrop-blur-xl backdrop-saturate-[1.6] h-full\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3 p-6 sm:p-8\"><h3 class=\"text-[1.75rem] leading-[1.08] font-medium tracking-[-0.025em] text-foreground\">Operational platforms</h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-7 text-foreground/68\">Internal systems, dashboards, and shared platforms that support ongoing product or business operations.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"rounded-[1.9rem] border border-border/70 bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,var(--surface-1),var(--surface-2))] shadow-[var(--shadow-soft)] backdrop-blur-xl backdrop-saturate-[1.6] h-full\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3 p-6 sm:p-8\"><h3 class=\"text-[1.75rem] leading-[1.08] font-medium tracking-[-0.025em] text-foreground\">Developer-facing products</h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-7 text-foreground/68\">APIs, tooling surfaces, documentation systems, and product experiences built for technical audiences.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"rounded-[1.9rem] border border-border/70 bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,var(--surface-1),var(--surface-2))] shadow-[var(--shadow-soft)] backdrop-blur-xl backdrop-saturate-[1.6] h-full\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3 p-6 sm:p-8\"><h3 class=\"text-[1.75rem] leading-[1.08] font-medium tracking-[-0.025em] text-foreground\">Open-source ecosystems</h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-7 text-foreground/68\">Public packages, templates, starter kits, and integration layers designed to invite contribution.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"rounded-[1.9rem] border border-border/70 bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,var(--surface-1),var(--surface-2))] shadow-[var(--shadow-soft)] backdrop-blur-xl backdrop-saturate-[1.6] h-full\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3 p-6 sm:p-8\"><h3 class=\"text-[1.75rem] leading-[1.08] font-medium tracking-[-0.025em] text-foreground\">High-trust web experiences</h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-7 text-foreground/68\">Marketing and product surfaces where clarity, credibility, and technical taste matter as much as polish.</p></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"section-space\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-full max-w-7xl px-5 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 space-y-10\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"max-w-3xl space-y-5\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full border px-3 py-1 text-[0.72rem] font-medium tracking-[0.13em] uppercase transition-colors border-border/70 bg-background/52 text-foreground/62 backdrop-blur-sm backdrop-saturate-[1.3]\">Project signals</div><div class=\"space-y-4\"><h2 class=\"section-title\">A few signs that the fit is right.</h2><p class=\"section-copy\">The work is strongest when technical structure matters as much as visible output.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"rounded-[1.9rem] border border-border/70 bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,var(--surface-1),var(--surface-2))] shadow-[var(--shadow-soft)] backdrop-blur-xl backdrop-saturate-[1.6] h-full\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3 p-6 sm:p-8\"><h3 class=\"font-medium tracking-[-0.025em] text-foreground text-xl\">Multiple audiences and complex interaction surfaces</h3></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"rounded-[1.9rem] border border-border/70 bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,var(--surface-1),var(--surface-2))] shadow-[var(--shadow-soft)] backdrop-blur-xl backdrop-saturate-[1.6] h-full\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3 p-6 sm:p-8\"><h3 class=\"font-medium tracking-[-0.025em] text-foreground text-xl\">Technical credibility is part of the brand experience</h3></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"rounded-[1.9rem] border border-border/70 bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,var(--surface-1),var(--surface-2))] shadow-[var(--shadow-soft)] backdrop-blur-xl backdrop-saturate-[1.6] h-full\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3 p-6 sm:p-8\"><h3 class=\"font-medium tracking-[-0.025em] text-foreground text-xl\">Shared structure needs to get stronger before the platform can scale</h3></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-18 sm:py-24\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-full max-w-7xl px-5 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"section-frame relative overflow-hidden px-6 py-10 sm:px-10 sm:py-12\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden rounded-[inherit]\"><div class=\"absolute top-0 left-[-35%] h-px w-1/2 bg-[linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,rgba(67,45,215,0.95),transparent)]\"></div></div><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 h-full w-full fill-current stroke-current hero-grid-mask text-foreground/12\"><defs><pattern id=\"_R_2kav5ulb_\" width=\"44\" height=\"44\" patternUnits=\"userSpaceOnUse\" x=\"-1\" y=\"-1\"><path d=\"M.5 44V.5H44\" fill=\"none\" stroke-dasharray=\"0\"></path></pattern></defs><rect width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" fill=\"url(#_R_2kav5ulb_)\"></rect><svg x=\"-1\" y=\"-1\" class=\"overflow-visible\"></svg></svg><div class=\"relative grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_auto] lg:items-end\"><div class=\"space-y-5\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full border px-3 py-1 text-[0.72rem] font-medium tracking-[0.13em] uppercase transition-colors border-primary/40 bg-primary text-white backdrop-blur-sm backdrop-saturate-[1.4]\">Project fit</div><h2 class=\"section-title max-w-3xl\">If the system needs technical structure and product-level finish, that is the right kind of brief.</h2><p class=\"section-copy max-w-xl\">Sonicverse is best used where long-term clarity matters as much as short-term delivery.</p></div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row lg:flex-col\"><a class=\"inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-full border font-medium whitespace-nowrap transition-all duration-200 outline-none select-none focus-visible:border-ring focus-visible:ring-3 focus-visible:ring-ring/40 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg]:size-4 border-transparent bg-[linear-gradient(135deg,#4d35ef_0%,#432dd7_100%)] text-white shadow-[0_14px_40px_rgba(67,45,215,0.28)] hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-[0_20px_54px_rgba(67,45,215,0.36)] h-12 px-6 text-[0.95rem]\" href=\"/contact\">Start a project</a><a class=\"inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-full border font-medium whitespace-nowrap transition-all duration-200 outline-none select-none focus-visible:border-ring focus-visible:ring-3 focus-visible:ring-ring/40 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg]:size-4 border-border/80 bg-background/52 text-foreground/84 ba